{"tid":1752603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"問題票呢樣嘢喺下次選舉前一定要搞到修例","createTime":"2019-11-24T22:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T13:23:19.000Z","uid":229369,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24560459e4bcb8af3e8140754548cf7e757d693e","tid":1752603,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:11:49.000Z","msg":"一定要喺圓圈內印一個剔先計！<br />\n<br />\n如果印出圓圈、印多過一個嘅話，點票時公開問題票就會知道某個目標受賄人士有無投某候選人：<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 行賄者叫受賄者喺1號候選人右上方印3個剔，點票時如果有呢張問題票就有着數畀佢 / 再離譜啲可以明張目膽叫人用個印印自己個名/代表編號上去都得<br />\n<br />\n如果下次選舉前政府唔改例，我哋全部人可以整到張張都係問題票，搞到政府要用幾日先點得晒票，迫使政府盡快修例！"},{"pid":"933602351f4d252ee2af63456baf5900df30a0c6","tid":1752603,"uid":229369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:12:29.000Z","msg":"推到廢老無着數！"},{"pid":"d2f169b0ff5925be1f7677d8d8d83aa7b3a15b80","tid":1752603,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:24:43.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d33b28a22fc79aabe538c4d059f5a80c57ea98e5","tid":1752603,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:24:53.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"e835e41f244ae554cc8bc54b86cb4cf54a9e3535","tid":1752603,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:25:06.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"c6258dd6e16e185ef57fc42f4e823a57ef2fc0bf","tid":1752603,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:25:16.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"c7b8c8aee63af5c27019cb91e63e2b9f3d1e3f86","tid":1752603,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:25:26.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"14c0168f71723ee47588a32f05e0671318d1cba2","tid":1752603,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:25:40.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"7eb65f5dc0a74216bcbd0ac4208c7059377a51de","tid":1752603,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:25:51.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pi